# Rayleigh-Benard convection at Ra = 1e5, Pr = 0.71
# Validation: De Vahl Davis (1983)
#
# Hot bottom, cold top, periodic side walls.
# Convection rolls develop above the critical Rayleigh number Ra_c ≈ 1708.
#
# Run via Julia API or `run_simulation("examples/rayleigh_benard.krk")`.

# The Preset already sets ν, Pr, Ra. Override the Run length and Output here.
Preset rayleigh_benard_2d

Run 30000 steps
Output vtk every 5000 [rho, ux, uy, T]
